<div class="banner">
    <h1>Asset management for .NET web apps</h1>
    <div class="about">
        <div class="intro">
            <p>Dumping your scripts into a folder is no way to manage your client-side code!</p>
            <p>Cassette automatically sorts, concatenates, minifies, caches and versions all your JavaScript, CoffeeScript, CSS, LESS and HTML templates.</p>
            <p>It's flexible, extensible and optimized for developer happiness.</p>
            <p class="last"><a class="call-to-action" href="@Url.RouteUrl("Download")">Download Now</a> Or read on to see Cassette in action...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="screencast">
            <p>Please note: Website still under development.</p>
            <p>Check back soon for videos and documentation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

